6
00:00:56,692 --> 00:00:59,153
Astaga, kenapa orang-orang
menyebutmu Penyihir Kecil?

7
00:00:59,946 --> 00:01:01,239
Mau kopi atau teh?

8
00:01:04,033 --> 00:01:04,867
Teh.

9
00:01:11,457 --> 00:01:14,335
- Kutunggu di ruang kerja.
- Baik.

10
00:01:26,514 --> 00:01:28,099
<i>Dan-i, kau di mana?</i>

11
00:01:28,432 --> 00:01:30,309
<i>Hae-rin mabuk dan datang lagi.</i>

12
00:01:31,018 --> 00:01:32,562
Aku di depan rumahmu.

13
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:41,529
<i>Benarkah? Aku masih di kantor.
Akan kuberi tahu saat pulang.</i>

14
00:01:55,877 --> 00:01:56,836
<i>Eun-ho.</i>

15
00:01:57,879 --> 00:02:00,214
<i>Ini surat ke-13 dariku.</i>

16
00:02:01,299 --> 00:02:03,801
<i>Setiap aku mabuk dan ke rumahmu,</i>

17
00:02:04,302 --> 00:02:07,263
<i>aku tulis surat dan menyembunyikannya
di rak bukumu.</i>

18
00:02:14,729 --> 00:02:16,856
<i>Kurasa kau belum baca satu pun.</i>

19
00:02:25,072 --> 00:02:26,741
<i>Katamu kau tinggal bersama wanita,</i>

20
00:02:28,576 --> 00:02:30,286
<i>tapi kuharap itu bohong.</i>

21
00:02:31,579 --> 00:02:33,331
<i>Dan meskipun itu benar,</i>

22
00:02:34,332 --> 00:02:36,751
<i>aku tak akan menyerah dengan mudah</i>

23
00:02:38,711 --> 00:02:40,338
<i>karena aku sudah</i>

24
00:02:40,671 --> 00:02:42,381
<i>jatuh cinta padamu.</i>

25
00:02:44,592 --> 00:02:46,719
<i>Aku tak bisa kendalikan perasaanku lagi.</i>

26
00:02:46,802 --> 00:02:48,054
<i>Itulah cinta.</i>

27
00:02:49,555 --> 00:02:50,681
<i>Aku mencintaimu, Eun-ho.</i>

28
00:02:52,642 --> 00:02:54,560
<i>Ini kali pertama aku mengatakan "cinta".</i>

29
00:02:55,061 --> 00:02:57,146
<i>Butuh 12 surat sebelum aku mengatakannya.</i>

30
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,231
Cepat.

31
00:03:05,238 --> 00:03:06,447
Aku tak punya tempat lain.

32
00:03:08,658 --> 00:03:09,867
Aku tak punya tempat lagi.

33
00:03:22,088 --> 00:03:23,339
Nona Daun Bawang.

34
00:03:28,135 --> 00:03:29,178
Sedang apa di sini?

35
00:03:31,722 --> 00:03:32,932
Apa aku

36
00:03:33,724 --> 00:03:35,476
juga baru turun dari bus?

37
00:03:36,435 --> 00:03:37,645
Apa?

38
00:03:43,901 --> 00:03:45,778
Prakiraan cuaca bilang besok hujan.

39
00:03:46,112 --> 00:03:48,030
Kita bicarakan panekuk daun bawang, ingat?

40
00:03:48,155 --> 00:03:48,990
Aku teringat itu.

41
00:03:49,073 --> 00:03:51,158
Seharusnya panekuk daun bawang.

42
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,463
Kurasa sudah mulai.

43
00:04:05,298 --> 00:04:06,132
Sepertinya begitu.

44
00:04:08,217 --> 00:04:09,343
Kebetulan sekali.

45
00:04:10,052 --> 00:04:11,721
Kenapa kita bisa berpapasan begini?

46
00:04:12,555 --> 00:04:14,056
Ditambah hujan juga.

47
00:04:15,182 --> 00:04:17,184
Kita ditakdirkan
makan panekuk daun bawang?

48
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,186
Mustahil.

49
00:04:20,021 --> 00:04:22,023
Omong-omong, sudah makan malam?

50
00:04:24,275 --> 00:04:26,485
- Kau?
- Ayo makan dulu.

51
00:04:33,242 --> 00:04:34,327
Tunggu.

52
00:04:35,036 --> 00:04:38,456
- Kau suka basah kuyup?
- Tidak, tapi...

53
00:04:39,206 --> 00:04:40,541
Kita tak punya payung.

54
00:04:40,624 --> 00:04:41,751
Kau bicara apa?

55
00:04:46,964 --> 00:04:48,174
Lihat pohon di sana?

56
00:04:49,467 --> 00:04:51,135
Tatap pohon itu sebentar.

57
00:04:51,218 --> 00:04:52,762
Aku akan ambil payung.

58
00:04:54,346 --> 00:04:55,765
Tidak ada toko dekat sini.

59
00:04:56,182 --> 00:04:58,225
Kau mau ambil payung di mana?

60
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,270
Sudah sepuluh detik.

61
00:05:06,025 --> 00:05:06,984
Dua puluh detik.

62
00:05:12,948 --> 00:05:14,075
Tiga puluh lima detik.

63
00:05:17,244 --> 00:05:19,246
- Dari mana ini?
- Sulap.

64
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,664
Ayo.

65
00:05:23,125 --> 00:05:24,043
Ayo.

66
00:05:37,932 --> 00:05:40,267
Teman serumahmu belum pulang?

67
00:05:40,351 --> 00:05:41,685
Katamu ada wanita.

68
00:05:41,769 --> 00:05:42,937
Kenapa kemari

69
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:44,146
jika tahu itu?

70
00:05:44,605 --> 00:05:47,441
Ayolah. Tampaknya kau
tak tinggal dengan siapa pun.

71
00:05:47,525 --> 00:05:48,484
- Benar.
- Tidak.

72
00:05:48,567 --> 00:05:50,277
Aku tinggal dengan seseorang.

73
00:05:54,281 --> 00:05:56,826
Tahu berapa pacar yang kau punya
sejak aku masuk Gyeoroo?

74
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,746
Astaga, aku populer.

75
00:06:01,705 --> 00:06:03,874
Tidak, itu berarti
kau diputuskan lima kali.

76
00:06:05,167 --> 00:06:07,837
Siapa yang menemani
saat kau diputuskan lima kali?

77
00:06:08,838 --> 00:06:09,880
Aku, Song Hae-rin.

78
00:06:09,964 --> 00:06:12,758
Setidaknya kau memacari tiga pria,
semuanya mencampakkanmu.

79
00:06:12,842 --> 00:06:13,884
Kita dicampakkan.

80
00:06:13,968 --> 00:06:16,512
- Kita berkencan saja?
- Aku tinggal dengan seseorang.

81
00:06:17,596 --> 00:06:19,265
Kapan kau akan diputuskan?

82
00:06:19,348 --> 00:06:20,641
Aku bisa menunggu.

83
00:06:20,724 --> 00:06:22,768
Astaga, kau bersikap konyol lagi.

84
00:06:23,602 --> 00:06:24,603
Harus diajari.

85
00:06:24,812 --> 00:06:25,646
Kemari.

86
00:06:25,729 --> 00:06:26,772
Astaga.

87
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,369
Astaga.

88
00:06:43,247 --> 00:06:45,374
Hae-rin, pulanglah. Hujan.

